trans-unit.source: Represents an error that occurs when the <see cref="M:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.IFormRegionFactory.GetFormRegionStorage(System.Object,Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.OlFormRegionMode,Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.OlFormRegionSize)" /> method of the form region factory class returns <see langword="null" />.
trans-unit.target: 表示在表单区域工厂类的 <see cref="M:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.IFormRegionFactory.GetFormRegionStorage(System.Object,Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.OlFormRegionMode,Microsoft.Office.Interop.Outlook.OlFormRegionSize)" /> 方法返回 <see langword="null" /> 时发生的错误。

trans-unit.source: The <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.IFormRegionFactory.GetFormRegionStorage%2A> of the form region factory class is called by Outlook only if the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.IFormRegionFactory.Kind%2A> property of the form region factory returns the <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.FormRegionKindConstants.Ofs> enumeration value.
trans-unit.target: <xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.IFormRegionFactory.GetFormRegionStorage%2A>窗体区域工厂类由 Outlook 才<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.IFormRegionFactory.Kind%2A>属性的窗体区域工厂返回<xref:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.FormRegionKindConstants.Ofs>枚举值。

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.FormRegionStorageNullException" /> class.
trans-unit.target: 初始化 <see cref="T:Microsoft.Office.Tools.Outlook.FormRegionStorageNullException" /> 类的新实例。
